cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF to '999.999.999.999' (invalid IP format) will cause network interface configuration failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting nrofDownlinkSymbols to 20 (exceeds maximum allowed symbols) will cause configuration validation failure in the TDD configuration.
du.explanation_zh: 將 nrofDownlinkSymbols 設定為 20（超過最大允許符號數）會在 TDD 配置中導致配置驗證失敗。
